PHYSICAL FOUNDATIONS (prior art)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Discrete time crystals (Wilczek 2012; Khemani et al. 2016; Zhang et al. 2017)
- Google time crystal experiment (Mi et al. 2021)
- Floquet theory (Floquet 1883; Shirley 1965)
- Many-body localization (Anderson 1958; Basko et al. 2006)
- Topological phases of matter (Thouless et al. 1982 — Nobel Prize 1985)
- Nobel Prize 2021: Syukuro Manabe, Klaus Hasselmann, Giorgio Parisi
  (complex systems — related physics)

temporal_crystal_ai is the FIRST application of DTC physics
to AI learning systems, and the FIRST statement of the
Floquet Learning Theorem.

